,Operational issues,Bind/Unbind Phone,Binding,,,How to bind a mobile phone.,"1. Enter the official account: ""Introduction"" - ""Personal Center"" - Bind your phone number (multiple numbers can be bound).
2. Alternatively, you can complete the binding by entering ""I want to bind + phone number"" in the official account chat box.",,,,
,,,Unbind,,,"I have linked two numbers, how do I unlink one of them?","If you have only linked one number, you can unbind it by unfollowing the official account. If you have linked multiple numbers, customer service can assist in unbinding a specific number. We will unbind the excess numbers through the backend system.",,,,
