,,,Merchant Information,,,How can I contact the seller?,"View through the public account: Go to the ""Order Food"" - ""Orders"" page, and click on ""Cancel Order"" to directly call the merchant. You can also click on the shop icon in the upper right corner of the merchant's page to view detailed information such as contact number and address.",,,,
,,,Container Position Administrator Information,,,How to check the information of the container position administrator?,"Check through the official account: Go to ""Campus Selection"" - ""Box Number"" page, and click to view the administrator information.",,,,
,,How to remotely open a box.,,,,"If I don't have the pickup code, can I still open the box remotely?","You can also provide your local number for the call, and after we confirm, we will remotely unlock the box for you through the system.",,,,
,,What is the storage time for takeout food?,,,,Can I extend the storage time of the meal?,"The normal storage time is 60 minutes. According to the regulations of the Market Supervision Administration, we only support the storage of fast food for 60 minutes and have repeatedly reminded both the food deliverer and the food receiver. To avoid food spoilage and ensure the cleanliness of the storage box, meals that are not picked up within the time limit may be cleared and discarded by the administrator.",,,,
,,How to handle erroneous top-ups.,,,,What should I do if I accidentally made the wrong recharge?,"If you accidentally recharge, we will process your refund request within 3 working days after verifying the information. If there are no delivery records for the account, a refund will be processed.",,,,
