,,,Unbind,,,"Can the phone number linked to the food delivery platform be unbound? If so, what are the specific steps?","If you have only linked one number, you can unbind it by unfollowing the official account. If you have linked multiple numbers, customer service can assist in unbinding a specific number. We will unbind the excess numbers through the backend system.","Unbind, public account",,,
