,,,Merchant information,,,Could you please provide me with the specific address of the merchant?,"View through the official account: Go to the ""Order Food"" - ""Orders"" page, and click on the order to directly call the merchant. You can also click on the shop icon in the upper right corner of the merchant's page to view detailed information such as contact number and address.","Official account, food ordering, merchant phone number.",,,
