,,How to remotely open a box.,,,,My situation is a bit特殊; I'm currently stuck and unable to open the delivery box. Can your customer service center help me open it?,"You can provide the pickup code or your phone number to call us, and we will remotely unlock the box for you after confirmation.","Pickup code, device number, remote unlocking.",,,
