,,What is the storage time for takeout food?,,,,"Do different types of takeout have varying storage times? If so, how long is it approximately?","The normal storage time is 60 minutes. According to the regulations of the Market Supervision Administration, we only support the storage of fast food for 60 minutes and have repeatedly reminded both the food deliverers and recipients. To avoid food spoilage and ensure the cleanliness of the storage compartments, meals that are not picked up within the time limit may be cleared and discarded by the administrators.","60 minutes, meal cleanup",,,
,,How to handle erroneous top-ups.,,,,How long will it take to get a resolution after an erroneous recharge?,"If you accidentally recharge, we will process your refund request within 3 working days after verifying the information. If there are no delivery records for the account, a refund will be processed.","Incorrect recharge, 3 working days, refund processing.",,,
